<br>
Depends on how you define great.  You have to make a comparison to determine if something is great or not.  <br>
<br>
In a way it does make it less great if you are comparing between shields.  If you are comparing from what is the best shield for that class, then the cleric shield dosn't have bearing on the other shields greatness. BUT!! while it makes for a nice sounding argument (verant uses it all the time btw) in practicality we do not measure this way.<br>
<br>
The hypocracy is made more clear if you exagerate the difference between the items.  Imagine the cleric shield kept its current stats but the best that a druid could get would be equivilent to a shiny brass shield.  <br>
<br>
Would you feel the same way about your shiny brass shield since it was the best you could get?  Naw you'd prolly become a cleric.<br>
<br>
While you would probably be a happier person if you didn't compare your equiptment with stuff you cant use, its just not gonna happen very often in the real world, and it should be a consideration to the game designers.<br>
<br>
anyhow thats my take on it. <p><p><br>-Kiliaan Spiritwind<br>Preserver of Tunare<br>Avatar of Raj Artair<br><EMBED src="http://216.74.111.86/~synastu/images/footer3.swf" quality=high bgcolor=#000000  WIDTH=300 HEIGHT=40 TYPE="application/x-shockwave-flash" PLUGINSPAGE="http://www.macromedia.com/shockwave/download/index.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash"></EMBED></p><i></i></td></tr></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessageRange?topicID=3193.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3325.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3274.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3193.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3193.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3193.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3193.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" ce